description: In this video, I show you how to make my Pumpkin and Peanut Butter Dog Treats. Just 3 ingredients to make these DIY dog treats. They are quick, easy, and so much more affordable to make healthy dog treats at home than to buy the pricey store-bought ones. And the best part, Chickpea dog loves them!!
name: Pumpkin & Peanut Butter Dog Treats - Just 3 Ingredients!
